Package: facomplex
Title: Methods for Assessing Factor Complexity in Factor Analysis Solutions
Version: 0.0.1.000
Authors@R: c(
  person("Merino-Soto", "Cesar A.", 
         email = "sikayax@yahoo.com.ar", 
         role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Dominguez-Lara", "Sergio",
         email = "sdominguezmpcs@gmail.com",
         role = c("ctb", "rev")))
Maintainer: Cesar Merino-Soto <sikayax@yahoo.com.ar>
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Description: Provides methods for estimating factor complexity coefficients in exploratory and confirmatory factor analysis (EFA/CFA) results. Included indices are the Hofman coefficient, its revised version, Fleming's approach for factorsimplicity , and others. Additional outputs include descriptive statistics (minimum, maximum, and mean) for target and non-target loadings, and visualization of results.
